+             * STABLE mapped cluster.  Classify it (capped, no per-free cost):
+             *   npgd>>maxsub  (many AS, few sub-PTEs each) => Contract-A large
+             *                  anon: mapcount-per-kernel-page is correct = FP.
+             *   maxsub~=PAGE_MMUCOUNT, refcount<tally => genuine per-sub-PTE
